description:
The model is in the original Ghibli style and can be used with other Loras in the generative animation style which can create fantastic scenes and buildings。

Download counterfeit-v2.5 model before use

If you are interested in the field of AIGC design, please join my channel to discuss it

Discordhttps://discord.gg/rX3UwAkQN2

v2.0 The light and shadow effect of the structure is optimized to be more friendly to the architectural expression. Please adjust Tag to avoid unreasonable building structure

v3.0 I improved the light, shadows and scenes, added a lot of detail, and tried to get away from the original style, which is more animation oriented. If you don't like this style, please continue to use v2.0, of course, if you want to try new style and details, you can try it

v4.0 Added more architectural style and more friendly for close-up shots. More details, of course, if you like the style of the previous three versions, please download free

If you have any questions, please contact me by email

This model is not for commercial use, only for exchange learning
